<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ru">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>SpravPortal Checker - Проверка номеров телефонов</title>
    
    <!-- Bootstrap 5 CSS -->
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <!-- Font Awesome Icons -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.0/css/all.min.css">
    
    <style>
        body {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1a1a2e 0%, #16213e 100%);
            min-height: 100vh;
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
        }
        
        .container-custom {
            max-width: 900px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        
        .card {
            border: none;
            border-radius: 20px;
            box-shadow: 0 20px 60px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);
            background: #0f3460;
            color: white;
        }
        
        .card-header {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #e94560 0%, #533483 100%);
            border-radius: 20px 20px 0 0 !important;
            padding: 30px;
            text-align: center;
            border-bottom: none;
        }
        
        .btn-check-phone {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #e94560 0%, #533483 100%);
            border: none;
            padding: 12px 30px;
            font-weight: bold;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }
        
        .btn-check-phone:hover {
            transform: scale(1.02);
            box-shadow: 0 5px 20px rgba(233, 69, 96, 0.4);
        }
        
        .info-card {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
            backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
            border-radius: 15px;
            padding: 20px;
            margin-top: 20px;
            animation: fadeIn 0.5s ease;
        }
        
        @keyframes fadeIn {
            from {
                opacity: 0;
                transform: translateY(20px);
            }
            to {
                opacity: 1;
                transform: translateY(0);
            }
        }
        
        .info-item {
            padding: 12px;
            border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
        }
        
        .info-item:last-child {
            border-bottom: none;
        }
        
        .info-label {
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #a8b2d1;
        }
        
        .info-value {
            color: white;
        }
        
        .security-badge {
            padding: 8px 20px;
            border-radius: 25px;
            font-weight: bold;
            display: inline-block;
        }
        
        .security-safe {
            background: #00b4d8;
            color: white;
        }
        
        .security-danger {
            background: #e94560;
            color: white;
        }
        
        .input-group-text {
            background: #533483;
            color: white;
            border: none;
        }
        
        .form-control {
            background: #1a1a2e;
            border: 1px solid #533483;
            color: white;
        }
        
        .form-control:focus {
            background: #1a1a2e;
            border-color: #e94560;
            box-shadow: 0 0 0 0.2rem rgba(233, 69, 96, 0.25);
            color: white;
        }
        
        .form-control::placeholder {
            color: #6c757d;
        }
        
        .alert-custom {
            border-radius: 10px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        
        .badge-mnp {
            background: #ffd166;
            color: #1a1a2e;
            padding: 5px 10px;
            border-radius: 20px;
            font-size: 12px;
        }
        
        .operator-badge {
            background: #533483;
            padding: 4px 12px;
            border-radius: 20px;
            font-size: 13px;
        }
        
        hr {
            border-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
        }
        
        code {
            background: #1a1a2e;
            padding: 4px 8px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            color: #e94560;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container-custom">
        <div class="card">
            <div class="card-header">
                <i class="fas fa-shield-alt fa-3x mb-3"></i>
                <h1 class="display-6 fw-bold">SpravPortal Checker</h1>
                <p class="lead">Проверка номеров через API v3 — спам, мошенники, оператор и регион</p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="card-body p-4">
                <!-- Форма ввода номера -->
                <form method="POST" action="/" class="mb-4">
                    <div class="input-group mb-3">
                        <span class="input-group-text">
                            <i class="fas fa-phone"></i>
                        </span>
                        <input type="tel" 
                               class="form-control form-control-lg" 
                               name="phone_number" 
                               placeholder="+7 (999) 123-45-67 или 89515200611"
                               required
                               value="{{ request.form.get('phone_number', '') }}">
                    </div>
                    
                    <button type="submit" class="btn btn-check-phone btn-lg w-100 text-white">
                        <i class="fas fa-search"></i> Проверить номер через SpravPortal
                    </button>
                </form>
                
                <!-- Flash сообщения -->
                {% with messages = get_flashed_messages(with_categories=true) %}
                    {% if messages %}
                        {% for category, message in messages %}
                            <div class="alert alert-{{ 'success' if category == 'success' else 'danger' }} alert-custom fade show" role="alert">
                                <i class="fas fa-{{ 'check-circle' if category == 'success' else 'exclamation-triangle' }}"></i>
                                {{ message }}
                            </div>
                        {% endfor %}
                    {% endif %}
                {% endwith %}
                
                <!-- Информация о номере -->
                {% if phone_info %}
                    <div class="info-card">
                        <h4 class="mb-3 text-center">
                            <i class="fas fa-info-circle"></i> Результат проверки
                        </h4>
                        
                        <!-- Безопасность - основной блок -->
                        <div class="info-item mb-3" style="background: rgba(0,0,0,0.2); border-radius: 10px;">
                            <span class="info-label">
                                <i class="fas fa-shield-alt"></i> Вердикт:
                            </span>
                            <span class="info-value">
                                <span class="security-badge security-{{ phone_info.security_class }}">
                                    <i class="fas {{ phone_info.security_icon }}"></i>
                                    {{ phone_info.security_status }}
                                </span>
                                {% if phone_info.spam_details %}
                                    <small class="text-muted ms-2">{{ phone_info.spam_details }}</small>
                                {% endif %}
                            </span>
                        </div>
                        
                        <div class="info-item">
                            <span class="info-label">
                                <i class="fas fa-phone-alt"></i> Номер:
                            </span>
                            <span class="info-value">
                                <code>{{ phone_info.phone_formatted }}</code>
                            </span>
                        </div>
                        
                        <div class="info-item">
                            <span class="info-label">
                                <i class="fas fa-globe"></i> Страна:
                            </span>
                            <span class="info-value">
                                <strong>{{ phone_info.country }}</strong>
                                {% if phone_info.country_code %}
                                    <span class="operator-badge">+{{ phone_info.country_code }}</span>
                                {% endif %}
                            </span>
                        </div>
                        
                        {% if phone_info.region %}
                        <div class="info-item">
                            <span class="info-label">
                                <i class="fas fa-map-marker-alt"></i> Регион:
                            </span>
                            <span class="info-value">{{ phone_info.region }}</span>
                        </div>
                        {% endif %}
                        
                        {% if phone_info.timezone %}
                        <div class="info-item">
                            <span class="info-label">
                                <i class="fas fa-clock"></i> Часовой пояс:
                            </span>
                            <span class="info-value">{{ phone_info.timezone }}</span>
                        </div>
                        {% endif %}
                        
                        <div class="info-item">
                            <span class="info-label">
                                <i class="fas fa-tower-cell"></i> Оператор:
                            </span>
                            <span class="info-value">
                                <span class="operator-badge">{{ phone_info.operator }}</span>
                                {% if phone_info.operator_code %}
                                    <small class="text-muted">(код {{ phone_info.operator_code }})</small>
                                {% endif %}
                            </span>
                        </div>
                        
                        <div class="info-item">
                            <span class="info-label">
                                <i class="fas fa-tag"></i> Тип линии:
                            </span>
                            <span class="info-value">{{ phone_info.line_type }}</span>
                        </div>
                        
                        {% if phone_info.mnp_transferred %}
                        <div class="info-item">
                            <span class="info-label">
                                <i class="fas fa-exchange-alt"></i> Перенос номера (MNP):
                            </span>
                            <span class="info-value">
                                <span class="badge-mnp">
                                    <i class="fas fa-arrow-right"></i> Перенесён от {{ phone_info.mnp_original_operator }}
                                </span>
                            </span>
                        </div>
                        {% endif %}
                        
                        {% if phone_info.spam_category %}
                        <div class="info-item">
                            <span class="info-label">
                                <i class="fas fa-tag"></i> Категория:
                            </span>
                            <span class="info-value">{{ phone_info.spam_category }}</span>
                        </div>
                        {% endif %}
                        
                        {% if phone_info.spam_reports > 0 %}
                        <div class="info-item">
                            <span class="info-label">
                                <i class="fas fa-flag"></i> Жалобы пользователей:
                            </span>
                            <span class="info-value">{{ phone_info.spam_reports }}</span>
                        </div>
                        {% endif %}
                        
                        {% if phone_info.has_comments %}
                        <div class="info-item">
                            <span class="info-label">
                                <i class="fas fa-comments"></i> Отзывы:
                            </span>
                            <span class="info-value">Есть отзывы на портале</span>
                        </div>
                        {% endif %}
                    </div>
                {% endif %}
                
                <!-- Информация об API -->
                <div class="mt-4 text-center">
                    <hr>
                    <p class="small text-muted">
                        <i class="fas fa-database"></i> Данные предоставлены SpravPortal API v3 — 
                        более 55 млн номеров, ежедневное обновление, проверка спама и мошенников
                    </p>
                    <p class="small text-muted">
                        <i class="fas fa-lock"></i> Источники: Реестр нумерации РФ, БДПН, база нежелательных номеров
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    
    <!-- Bootstrap JS -->
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
